      <scopecontent encodinganalog="520$a">
        <head>Scope and Content
</head>
        <p>Books, cards, letters, envelopes, and other items printed by Leonard F. Bahr (1938-1992), founder and owner of the Adagio Press from 1957-1988; biographical material of various dates about Bahr, check lists of Adagio press items; and a letter to Bahr from Henry Morris and two letters to Norman Forgue from Bahr. The Adagio Press was started in 1956 in Bahr's hometown of Harper Woods, Michigan.
</p>
      </scopecontent>
    </descgrp>
